Such portion or portions of the land herein reserved for housing purposes that are being used or earmarked for public or quasi-public purposes shall be excluded from such disposition.

Except in favor of the government or any of its branches or agencies, all lands disposed under this Proclamation shall not be subject to alienation and encumbrances for a term of ten years (10) from the issuance of the title in the case of sale or execution of contract in case of lease, nor shall they become liable to the satisfaction of any debt contracted prior to the expiration of said period, but the same, together with the improvements thereon, may be mortgaged to the Home Development Mutual Fund (Pag-Ibig).

The integration of the subject area to the present DOJ housing project shall be administered by the Department of Justice.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 29th day of May in the year of Our Lord Two Thousand and Six.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

